---
title: Sweet Potato Chickpea Curry with Baby Spinach over Basmati Rice
description: If there is a recipe of ours that most embodies the word nourishing, this might be it. At its center are vitamin-A-rich sweet potatoes and spinach, along with protein-packing chickpeas. But there’s also something positively soul-warming about its coconut milk sauce infused with garam masala’s warm, spicy overtones. You’ll know it’s special as it simmers on the stove, releasing incredible aromatics throughout your kitchen.
